The Blades reform as dragon-hunters
The Way of the Voice is lost
The Greybeards never forgive
Esbern and Delphine are satisfied but haunted
Paarthurnax Spared (Blades Left):
Paarthurnax leads dragons toward peace
Some follow, some don't
Skyrim has dragon allies and enemies
The Blades are gone forever
Esbern dies bitter
The Way of the Voice endures
Paarthurnax Spared (Esbern Convinced):
Paarthurnax leads dragons toward peace
